{"tid":2266474,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"變種病毒 20A.EU1 肆虐歐洲  專家：未來數月影響全球","createTime":"2020-11-01T10:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T23:26:37.000Z","uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"61fe8bbf92ebde58a3d8987262b1b956e13eea31","tid":2266474,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:42:30.000Z","msg":"生活　健康<br />\n發佈時間<br />\n2 小時前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4MTnJAz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4MTnJAz.png&h=20c65784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫情在歐洲多國仍然持續，而部分國家以及城市更正遭受第二波疫情肆虐，據一項新研究表示，病毒已經變種並蔓延到整個歐洲大陸，而美國免疫學家、現任美國國家過敏和傳染病研究所主任 Anthony Stephen Fauci 亦表示，在未來幾個月內，疫情將不會停止，且將為全球帶來災難性的影響。<br />\n<br />\n目前歐洲疫情仍然不受控，甚至正在惡化。昨日（29 日）有瑞士和西班牙的研究團隊發表一項新研究，指發現自 6 月起，有起源於西班牙的武漢肺炎病毒變種為「20A.EU1」，並指自 7 月以來，西班牙記錄到的新變種的頻率已超過 40%，9 月更在瑞士、愛爾蘭、英國等地方錄得至少 70% 頻率，可謂瘋狂蔓延到整個歐洲大陸。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，美國疫情也持續惡化，該國病例持續新增，紐約確診病例已超過 50 萬。研究指目前尚不清楚該變種病毒是因為病毒傳播優勢，抑或是西班牙的遊客傳播。而美國免疫學家、現任美國國家過敏和傳染病研究所主任 Anthony Stephen Fauci 亦表示，疫情將在未來幾個月內帶來很大的影響。<br />\n<br />\nFauci 指，大城市的醫療資源相當不錯，但西北和中部州份將面臨極大的困難。他警告，美國的防疫在現階段並不樂觀，並指目前的防疫方向錯誤，如果繼續下去，美國可能需要面對死亡率大幅上升的困境。"},{"pid":"bb61dfa30f16ae7e3105a57d2cd95da047ff0bfc","tid":2266474,"uid":235152,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"印度神童又中"},{"pid":"7d22f6b62126f1f966857ee1775d4d32eb418a3a","tid":2266474,"uid":66365,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"COVID 20  歐洲肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bccbeb1af74a60d7641ffcdb3cbd10b8fef3ee","tid":2266474,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6baaaec2bb905814dc520ca607e98a3dfb5fd2a1","tid":2266474,"uid":358542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:11:45.000Z","msg":"西班牙流感2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c9f642c41c536b5e6601577132262391912d36","tid":2266474,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b226672e749b2bf641d74fb7c806d7dece5715","tid":2266474,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:17:49.000Z","msg":"睇嚟未來o個一年都要繼續戴口罩"},{"pid":"0068f3759179f2a0578ea8a0aef5d28875aaf1f4","tid":2266474,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:30:00.000Z","msg":"西班牙肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dceeaaf2e51c85e2d01b0b3dad1de65e3af5a62","tid":2266474,"uid":307265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T23:26:37.000Z","msg":"印度神童講嘅12月大災難應該冇錯"}]}